YOU ARE THE FINAL BOSS.

Pick your Dungeon Boss â€“ many unique playable bosses (with more to come!).

Quick and Addictive Runs â€“ Less than 30 minutes per game.

Endless Replayability â€“ Create your own builds with a vast variety of Attacks, Weapons, Active Powers, Items, Characters, and Minions.

Emergent Gameplay & Theorycrafting â€“ Discover unique effect combinations and synergies to crush hero raids.

Wave-Based Carnage â€“ Smash waves of Noobs in increasingly intense battles lasting from 20 to 90 seconds, and take down as many as you can.
